Package: galileantools
Title: Tools for Galilean Transformations and Projectile Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Ibrahima", "OURBANI DOUBLA MAMOUDOU", email = "ibrahimadoubla21@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to apply Galilean transformations, simulate projectile motion 
    from moving platforms, estimate platform velocity using observed trajectories,
    and visualize results.
